name: Sun Go Kong
description:
Wukong possess extra-ordinary power: immense strength, immortality, shape shifting abilities, possession of a giant staff that he can expand and shrinks at his command, ability to travel using clouds, Have eyes that can see the true form of a demon & Can change the hair on each body as an item or creature as a weapon or Army of war.

The mighty One Man Army, the Monkey King capable of wreaking havoc in Heaven, Even the Buddha himself had to face Sun Wukong,
With All His Ability He Has The capability To Destroy But He Also Has The Ability To Relax!
